More IQA Intraatomic ("Self") Energy Components:
-----------------------------------------------
  V_IQA_Intra(A) = Vne(A,A) + Vee(A,A)
                 = VC_IQA_Intra(A) + VX_IQA_Intra(A)
                 = Potential Energy Contribution to E_IQA_Intra(A)
                 = E_IQA_Intra(A) - T(A)
  VC_IQA_Intra(A) = Vne(A,A) + VeeC(A,A)
                  = Coulomb Potential Energy Contribution to E_IQA_Intra(A)
                  = E_IQA_Intra(A) - T(A) - VeeX(A,A)
  VX_IQA_Intra(A) = VeeX(A,A)
                  = Exchange-Correlation Energy Contribution to E_IQA_Intra(A)
                  = E_IQA_Intra(A) - T(A) - VC_IQA_Intra(A)
See "2EDM Note" and "DFT Note".
